# Third-Party Notices

This file enumerates the direct dependencies of `reconstruction`
and the license terms under which their upstream projects make them
available. Transitive dependencies inherit their license terms from
these direct parents.

Unlike a single-package component, `reconstruction` is a collection of
independently containerized modules under `modules/v2d_*/`, each with its
own `lib/pyproject.toml` and install. There is therefore no single
`uv.lock`: the versions below reflect each module's `pyproject.toml` /
install at release time and may be approximate. The SPDX license
identifier and copyright holder are the authoritative parts of each
entry; for the precise license terms and exact pinned version of any
individual package, consult the upstream project URL and the relevant
module's `pyproject.toml`.

